articles.title: Elderly man clutters whole flat with newspapers, volunteers carefully pick out cash hidden in the pile
articles.content: "Uncle had been sleeping on newspapers for over a decade. When they got dirty, he simply laid fresh ones on top. Layer after layer, year after year," it wrote.
